Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:21.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,A girl from the 9th grade's class 3 died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:23.43,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.44,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Her umbrella flew out of her hand \Nwhen she fell down the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:28.20,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,impaling her through the throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:29.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:31.97,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,It was so horrific, the witnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:33.63,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,were ordered never to speak of it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:35.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't she a class officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:39.56,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I heard her mother died in \Nan accident that same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:42.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:43.62,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:45.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's the school's most famous secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:47.90,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The curse of class 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:50.23,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,and the story that started \Nit all 26 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.33,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:54.25,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean it's going to \Nhappen again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:57.71,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe. Nothing happened last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:01.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Once it starts, somebody \Ndies every month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:04.00,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, at least one person \Nconnected to the class
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:06.00,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,dies per month.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Not just students?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.06,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,They say family members \Nare at risk, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:10.97,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Especially parents and siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:13.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know a lot about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:16.26,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,One of the guys in my kendo \Nclub is in class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:18.38,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,He told me in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:21.22,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't seem to believe it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:24.05,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But someone's actually died...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.05,0:01:25.17,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:28.69,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably best to stay \Naway from that class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:29.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.74,Default,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}June 2 (Tue.)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:19.72,Default,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Redial: Teshigawara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:38.26,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how's that lung of yours doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.86,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It seems fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:44.25,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,But you witnessed such an awful sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:45.95,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,That sort of thing can affect the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.04,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.45,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,My kid brother told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:53.96,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's in your class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.46,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Takeru Mizuno. He plays basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:58.46,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.25,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Here for a checkup?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.27,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.65,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's talk after it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:06.97,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I should be home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.62,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,My night shift ended hours ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.63,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,but things keep coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:13.96,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Something weird is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.71,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,And there was that other incident, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:20.11,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who died here in April?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.71,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to think too much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.78,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,If you do have to be hospitalized again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.71,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to take \Nextra good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.81,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Thanks in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.24,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:38.69,Default,Doctor,0000,0000,0000,,I see nothing that should \Naffect regular school attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.92,Default,Doctor,0000,0000,0000,,However, no strenuous activities just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.20,Default,Doctor,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep an eye on things \Nfor one more month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:45.61,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.03,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.65,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.59,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you won't have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.10,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,to take care of me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:00.21,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:04.38,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little late, but do you \Nwant to grab lunch somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:11.21,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,So, Misaki Fujioka was the cousin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:14.01,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,of that girl with the eyepatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:20.95,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I rarely talk with my kid brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.48,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,but he did tell me a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:26.92,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,It seems your class has \Nsome special circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.28,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Special circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:29.69,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:32.70,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't give me details, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:34.88,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.39,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The "circumstances"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.36,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain there's something going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.85,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,but nobody will tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.10,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:49.05,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,My brother seemed to \Nbe scared of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.46,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a hunch, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:56.25,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks what happened last \Nweek wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.04,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Not an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.59,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why he's scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.12,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.21,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:16.98,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, have you heard of \Nsomeone named Mei Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.06,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:21.46,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Misaki? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.72,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,A girl in class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.38,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Has your brother ever mentioned her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:31.36,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, he and I don't talk much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.71,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, the girl with the \Neyepatch that I told you about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.72,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,is named Mei Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:38.95,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:43.24,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,So, what, you like this Mei girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.28,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.50,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, something's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.77,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Something about her is different
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.22,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,from the rest of my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.22,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you call "liking" someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.46,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.57,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:03.31,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's so different about this Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:04.79,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:08.86,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,She's sort of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.76,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.65,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,she was being bullied by the other kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.54,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:19.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It seems more like \Nthey're scared of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.07,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.25,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not exactly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:27.38,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,One of the guys told me not \Nto mess with things that "don't exist."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:28.96,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:33.40,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,She claims nobody else \Nin the class can see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.97,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The accident last week
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.10,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,happened right after she told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.30,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it logically,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.01,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,it seems like simple coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:47.00,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to connect \Nthose two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.11,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:52.26,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,There's one other thing \Nthat bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.82,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,They say it happened 26 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.51,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Had you heard that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.50,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.64,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I went to South Middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.82,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know what it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.43,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,has to do with all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.99,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't help thinking \Nthere's a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:20.93,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:26.02,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's turning into quite the horror story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:29.69,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to ask my brother about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.35,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to school tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:32.63,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:35.30,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call if I find anything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:36.90,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,When's your next checkup?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.92,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,This Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.03,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,June 6, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:45.54,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure there's no \NDamien in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:48.63,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,But still, let's both be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:52.26,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Especially where unusual \Naccidents are concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:04.53,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm pretty sure there's no \NDamien in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.39,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:10.07,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look who I found!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.78,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.75,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya, Kouichi! Skipping school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:17.59,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just left the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.74,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.38,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.36,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.00,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite the actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:35.24,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say it, but \NI'm happy you think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:36.71,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:40.89,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it means my hard work in \Nthe club is paying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:42.47,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Which club?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.73,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,To be, or not to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:47.74,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0} is the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.41,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're in the theater club?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:52.27,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! With Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.03,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Izumi, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.90,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi Akazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.91,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,She tends to be a bit dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.38,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,It shows in her acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:04.32,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,But she's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.63,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,So I hope you'll help her out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:09.88,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:29.23,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,No... No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.15,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.89,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:50.46,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Hollow Eyes of Yomi at Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:09.77,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:15.78,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,My, it's unusual to see \Na boy your age here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:19.20,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a customer? Or perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.43,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.11,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a junior high student?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.23,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll give you half price.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:24.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:28.29,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time looking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:31.65,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:08.09,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Fancy meeting you here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.29,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:14.27,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was on my way home \Nfrom the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:17.10,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,and I just happened to walk by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:20.32,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? \NDidn't you go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:22.80,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I only go when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.80,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.93,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I won't have to be re-admitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.28,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,How's the class doing since, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:34.84,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.69,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,They're all terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:38.90,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:41.52,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,They think it's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.61,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What has?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:48.20,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Deep inside, they may have \Nonly half-believed it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.24,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.70,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Despite what they said to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:57.05,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they fully believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:01.39,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like it really is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:05.61,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it's 100% likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:09.80,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,...that it's already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:11.53,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:18.63,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.15,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,All the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:24.21,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It might be best for \Nyou to never find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.90,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Once you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.18,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what happened to class 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:33.21,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going back to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:35.16,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:40.28,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Then I probably shouldn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:41.99,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.28,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.63,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misa—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.29,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:20.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:23.36,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Good morning, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.62,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:31.30,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:40.67,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.92,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.94,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I've been getting them a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.41,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.66,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're tired, on more than one level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:54.41,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.61,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.35,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You said there's a right time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.30,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,to find out about things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.19,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell when that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.51,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:17.13,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um... So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.31,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What 9th grade class were you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:22.73,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,In 9th grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.65,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:26.12,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Class 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:28.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, did people talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:31.83,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,class 3 being cursed in your year, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.62,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.29,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,It was 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:40.65,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to \Nschool tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:44.08,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the tips I gave \Nyou for handling Yomi North?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:44.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.88,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Including number three?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.88,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. And number four, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Number three was to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:54.61,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,always uphold the class rules, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:56.80,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:00.62,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.31,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The third thing I needed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.43,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. It's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:08.19,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Always uphold the class rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:10.29,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.26,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:15.57,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I really am exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.53,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:18.91,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:21.41,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:23.08,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:26.92,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand that damn bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:34.95,Default,Board,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}June 3 (Wed.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:46.27,Default,Ouji,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi used the west \Nstaircase, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:50.27,Default,Saruta,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she use one so far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:53.58,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,She must've had a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.24,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Takako said she saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:58.28,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Takako Sugiura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.09,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,What did she see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.04,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,When Kouichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:18.89,Default,Nakao,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly thought it wouldn't \Nhappen this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:21.27,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,There are two possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.57,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,It's not happening this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.78,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,and Yukari's death was \Njust a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:29.79,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Either that, or it started in May.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.03,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,As the head of countermeasures,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:34.96,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't rely on wishful thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.13,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be one thing if it was just Yukari,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.33,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,but her mom died, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:43.30,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Because he broke the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:48.79,Default,Nakao,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they put a new \Nstudent in class 3, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.81,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It was convenient for the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.94,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The new principal still
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:55.55,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't fully understand our situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.43,Default,Nakao,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't the teachers explain it to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:03.57,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,They may have thought it was \Nbest to keep it among the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.81,Default,Nakao,0000,0000,0000,,So even the teachers want \Nnothing to do with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:10.23,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I was absent \Nhis first day here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:14.22,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If I had warned him in advance, \Nthis wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:18.39,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,What's done is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.89,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,The question is, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:24.45,Default,Nakao,0000,0000,0000,,And how do we let him know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:28.21,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be difficult to \Nexplain it to him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:31.25,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,And explaining it poorly \Ncould be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:34.06,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like getting caught in our own trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.64,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is a lot like the situation \Nthis class was in two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:44.15,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean we need \Nnew countermeasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.51,Default,Boy1,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:30.94,Default,Boy2,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.57,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:48.86,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:49.74,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:52.33,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "uh" me. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:57.81,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to call you all week,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:58.91,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,but you never answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:01.89,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Bad timing and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:04.35,Default,Teshigarara,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you were sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:08.60,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you'd tell me in June.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:13.31,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned "the first year," too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.40,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:17.26,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on, okay, Sakaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.52,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.56,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.11,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.78,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! The situation has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:29.90,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, it's up to the head
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:32.48,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,of countermeasures to handle this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:35.11,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,But things got complicated because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:37.10,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,this guy acted on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:37.97,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.30,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to pretend he \Nnever made that promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.38,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. As a favor to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:46.69,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, to the whole class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.48,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:56.02,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You said it's dangerous to mess \Nwith things that don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:57.72,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.91,Default,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Incoming Call: Mizuno
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.12,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.00,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.88,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.39,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Are you on lunch break right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:08.29,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:09.64,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:10.06,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have time to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:12.83,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Do you realize what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:11.68,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:15.50,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to check with \Nyou on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:17.96,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We have enough to worry about as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.28,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Check on what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:23.29,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,About the girl you told me \Nabout yesterday, Mei Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:26.35,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Does she really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:29.40,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:30.93,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Is she nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:32.56,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,For sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:34.01,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:37.63,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't come to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:38.93,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,So she's not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:41.24,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:44.57,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I spoke to my brother yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:47.51,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,He refuses to talk about \Nthe incident 26 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:49.87,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,or the accident last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:53.40,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,But when I asked him about Mei,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:55.24,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,his demeanor suddenly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:56.67,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,"What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.58,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,There's no girl like that in our class!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:00.54,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,He was adamant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.61,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,But that's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:05.25,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,He was dead serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.25,0:22:06.95,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,and he has no reason to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:08.09,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Misaki exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:09.60,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.34,0:22:12.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.57,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I just got on the \Nelevator, from the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:16.07,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.07,0:22:18.04,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that explains the static.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:19.30,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,But this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:32.66,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuno, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:33.59,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.92,0:24:50.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Build limbs.
